{"tid":1048970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌你老母]民主黨果然係民建聯第二梯隊","createTime":"2019-03-06T03:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T03:16:27.000Z","uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da108931d96ba6794bccb319c6628d829fbed6ab","tid":1048970,"uid":14256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"當正已經立左法咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背後代表佢地已經承認台灣係大陸一部份咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申往台灣與各黨派立委商討逃犯條例<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=339826&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D339826%26refer%3DShare&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=5fe89f96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D339826%26refer%3DShare&h=ab6239ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=339826&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員涂謹申啟程往台灣，與陸委會在內的政府部門、時代力量、國民黨等各黨派立委會面，商討本港修訂《逃犯條例》事宜及了解台灣對大律師公會建議的看法。 <br />\n<br />\n立法會議員涂謹申：「希望更了解他們情況，包括大律師公會的建議，延展司法管轄權，屆時在香港審理台灣發生的案件他們會否反對。反過來，我們要靠他們證據例如驗屍、化驗，甚至會有有人過來作證等，將表面上是台灣發生案件在香港審理，他們的態度如何？會否充分合作？」"}]}